\sum_ {n = 0}^{\infty} \frac{\sin n }{ 5^n} 
\sum_{n=0}^{\infty} |\frac{\sin n}{5^n}| \le \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{1}{5^n}= \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}(\frac{1}{5})^n=\frac{1}{1-\frac{1}{5}}=\frac{5}{4}
